            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1639415341258-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
