          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1639415341258-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong> and <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Slice half your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>into rounds (save them for garnish!), then chop the <strong>remaining chilli finely</strong></p><p>Once the onion has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger </strong>and <strong>chopped red chilli[es]</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 2-3 min further</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-onion-and-sliced-garlic-in-a-pan--1646222530630-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-onion-and-sliced-garlic-in-a-pan--1646222530630-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-onion-and-sliced-garlic-in-a-pan--1646222530630-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-onion-and-sliced-garlic-in-a-pan--1646222530630-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Chopped-onion-and-sliced-garlic-in-a-pan--1646222530630-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the garlic and ginger is softening, peel and chop your <strong>sweet potato[es] </strong>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped sweet potato</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until beginning to lightly brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1639415347151-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1639415347151-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
