          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1639415352642-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an intial 10 min, add your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>to the pan and cook for 2 min further or until refreshed and crunchy – this is your <strong>nutty sweet potato & sugar snap curry</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, chop your<strong> coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Remove the <strong>mango-glazed peanuts</strong> from the fridge and chop them roughly</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639415355571-x200.jpg",
