          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>nutty sweet potato & sugar snap curry</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Top with the<strong> chilli rounds</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!), <strong>chopped mango-glazed peanuts</strong> and <strong>chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
